			  	<h3>Comic Books</h3>
			  	<p id="adapleft">The Wheel of Time Series has been recreated as a series of comic books. These are written and drawn by Chuck Dixon and Chase Conley, and published on a monthly basis by Dynamite Entertainment.<br>So far, the prequel book A New Spring and Book one The Eye of the World have been published in a total of 43 issues.</p>
