			  	<h3>Games</h3>
			  	<p id="adapright">A text-based, multiplayer, real-time virtual world set around 30 years before the main series has been in continuous online operation since 1993.<br> A Computer Game(see above image) was released in 1999, in which an un-named Aes Sedai must track down a thief of the White Tower. Jordan was consulted on the project but did not write any of the plot and the game is not considered canon.<br>A Roleplaying game based on the Dungeons & Dragons d20 format was released in 2001. Jordan cited various issues with the storyline of this adaptation that contradicts the books.</p>
