			  	<h3>Television Adaptation</h3>
			  	<p id="adapright">A live-action adaptation of the series has been in the works since 2000. The rights have changed hands multiple times with talks of telivision miniseries and full-budget movie series being developed at various times.<br>Currently, Sony is handing the adaptation in a co-development deal with Amazong Studios to produce a TV Series. Casting is currently underway with Rosemund Pike signed on to play Moiraine.</p>
