		  	<h2>Conventions</h2>
		  	<img id="sideimgwide" src="images/dragon-con.jpg" alt="Curved block capitals write 'Dragon Con' across a blue and black circle with a yellow simplified dragon in flight inside the circle.">
		  	<p><strong>Dragon Con</strong><br>Dragon Con is a massive Sci-Fi and Fantasy Convention. Since the mid-80s the convention has been held yearly inviting fans of all of the largest sci-fi and fantasy movies, tv series, books and games. The Wheel of Time had an exclusive content track from 2001 through to 2012.</p>
		  	<img id="sideimgwide" src="images/jordan-con.jpg" alt="Jordan Con is shown in multi-coloured block capitals above the date, location and details of the 2019 convention. To the left of the details stands a dark-skinned woman with hair made of light and a dress made of crystals. She is holding a crystal mask that appears to be breaking.">
		  	<p><strong>Jordan Con</strong><br>In 2009, a group of fans came together in honour of the late Robert Jordan, to throw the first Jordan Con. Since then it has become a yearly event, building to include a large number of franchises from movies, tv shows, books and games. Panel Discussions merge different worlds or pit them against each other, with activities and events including Cosplay Contents, Karaoke, etc.</p>
